Pornind de la ideea unui calculator clasic pe care fiecare il are acasa, am creat acest program care imita comportamentul clasic al unui instrument de calcul. Operatiile sunt urmatoarele: - + / * ^, unde ^ este ridicare la putere. Programul te intreaba cate elemente vrei sa calculezi, spre exemplu daca vrei sa calculezi 1+2+3+4, tastezi 4. Dupa ce ai tastat numarul de elemente, scrii exact valorile si operandul, fara spatii intre ele, de forma 1+2*3/4 si la final se va afisa calculul, urmat de = rezultat.

Starting from the idea of a classic computer that everyone has at home, I created this program that imitates the classic behavior of a computing tool. The operations are the following: - + / * ^, where ^ is exponentiation. The program asks you how many elements you want to calculate, for example if you want to calculate 1+2+3+4, type 4. After typing the number of elements, write the exact values and the operand, without spaces between them, in the form 1+2 *3/4 and at the end the calculation will be displayed, followed by = result.
